Transaction¶

activeLedger python sdk provide a easy access to activledger funtinalities for Python developers, this documentation includes all the functions for this sdk.

The easiest way to use this sdk is through pip:

pip install activeLedger-sdk

Python Versions¶

Please note that only python 3.5+ version is supported
